      <title>奢侈品消费放缓导致 LVMH 销售额增长下滑</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/lvmhs-first-quarter-sales-growth-slips-3-luxury-slowdown-2024-04-16/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[路威酩轩集团第一季度的销售放缓，原因是价格上涨促使更多渴望拥有其奢侈品牌的消费者不再花费数千美元购买手袋和其他配饰。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/lvmhs-first-quarter-sales-growth-slips-3-luxury-slowdown-2024-04-16/</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 16 Apr 2024 15:50:01 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
